/-- If `F` reflects isos and `F.map f` is an iso, then `f` is an iso. -/
theorem is_iso_of_reflects_iso {A B : C} (f : «expr ⟶ » A B) (F : «expr ⥤ » C D) [IsIso (F.map f)]
    [reflects_isomorphisms F] : IsIso f :=
  reflects_isomorphisms.reflects F f
#align is_iso_of_reflects_iso is_iso_of_reflects_iso
